SUMMARY:Arashiyama Bamboo Grove
DESCRIPTION:Still beating the 10 AM tour bus rush. Walk through quickly — atmosphere drops the busier it gets.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Arashiyama%20Bamboo%20Grove%2C%2035.0166%2C135.6717
LOCATION:35.0166\,135.6717
