DTSTAMP:20260614T124021Z
DTSTART:20251203T040000Z
DTEND:20251203T051000Z
SUMMARY:Lunch in Arashiyama town
DESCRIPTION:Walk back down toward Togetsukyo. Yudofu (tofu hot pot) is the Arashiyama signature — try Shoraian or Yudofu Sagano. Or grab matcha soba at Arashiyama Yoshimura with bridge views.\n~2500 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Lunch%20in%20Arashiyama%20town%2C%2035.0148%2C135.6779
LOCATION:Arashiyama\, Ukyo Ward\, Kyoto
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Lunch%20in%20Arashiyama%20town%2C%2035.0148%2C135.6779
GEO:35.0148;135.6779
