SUMMARY:National Art Center
DESCRIPTION:Kurokawa's wavy glass facade — the building itself is the attraction even if the rotating exhibit doesn't grab you. Free to wander the atrium + cone-shaped cafe inside.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=National%20Art%20Center%2C%2035.6651%2C139.7268
LOCATION:35.6651\,139.7268
