SUMMARY:Shibuya Scramble Crossing
DESCRIPTION:Walk across Tokyo's iconic intersection — 3\,000 people per light cycle. Take the photo from the Starbucks above (Tsutaya 2F\, free). 3 min walk to the Hachiko statue. 20-30 min total before going up Sky.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shibuya%20Scramble%20Crossing%2C%2035.6595%2C139.7004
LOCATION:Shibuya Crossing\, Shibuya City
