SUMMARY:Bar High Five · nightcap
DESCRIPTION:Hidetsugu Ueno's legendary Ginza bar — 5 min walk from Hashimoto. Classic cocktails\, no music\, intimate counter. Reservation strongly recommended. ¥3-4K per cocktail. The full-stop on the best night of the trip.\n~5000 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Bar%20High%20Five%20%C2%B7%20nightcap%2C%2035.671%2C139.7641
LOCATION:Efflore Ginza 5 Building B1\, 5-4-15 Ginza\, Chuo City
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Bar%20High%20Five%20%C2%B7%20nightcap%2C%2035.671%2C139.7641
GEO:35.671;139.7641
END:VEVENT
