DTEND:20251207T225500Z
SUMMARY:Tsukiji Outer Market
DESCRIPTION:The original fish-market site (the auction moved to Toyosu but the outer market stayed). Best between 7-9 AM. Sushi-for-breakfast vibes\, knife shops\, tamago skewers\, tuna nigiri at counter pace. Walking distance to Ginza for the rest of the day.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Tsukiji%20Outer%20Market%2C%2035.6655%2C139.7707
LOCATION:Tsukiji Outer Market\, 4 Chome Tsukiji\, Chuo City
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Tsukiji%20Outer%20Market%2C%2035.6655%2C139.7707
GEO:35.6655;139.7707
END:VEVENT
