SUMMARY:Endo Sushi (Tsukiji)
DESCRIPTION:Sushi for breakfast — the Tsukiji ritual. ¥3000-5000 pp set menus\, sit at the counter\, watch the chef work. Lines move fast 8-9 AM.\n~4000 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Endo%20Sushi%20(Tsukiji)%2C%2035.6661%2C139.7703
